Titolo: Super Mario Party

Anno: 2018

Descrizione: Super Mario Party is a party video game developed by NDcube and published by Nintendo for the Nintendo Switch. The eleventh main entry in the Mario Party series, this game was described as a "complete refresh" of the franchise, bringing back and revitalizing gameplay elements from older titles while also introducing new ones to go along with them. It was released worldwide on 5 October 2018 and sold 1.5 million copies by the end of the month. As of december 2021, the game has sold more than 17.39 million copies worldwide, making it one of the top ten best-selling games on the system. A follow up title for the Nintendo Switch, Mario Party Superstars, was announced and released in 2021.

Genere: Party 

Valutazione: 76
